  "title": "UAT Operations #ESY",
  "description": "<p>•\tCollaborate with business analysts, project managers, and end-users to understand business requirements and acceptance criteria.</p><p>•\tDevelop and execute UAT test plans, test cases, and test scripts based on business requirements.</p><p>•\tCoordinate and facilitate UAT testing sessions with end-users and stakeholders.</p><p>•\tIdentify, document, and track defects and issues found during UAT.</p><p>•\tCommunicate test results and provide feedback to development and SD teams.</p><p>•\tEnsure that all business requirements are met before product release.</p><p>•\tAssist in the preparation of UAT test environments and data.</p><p>•\tSupport the resolution of issues and re-test fixes as needed.</p><p>•\tMaintain detailed documentation of test cases, results, and defect logs.</p><p>•\tParticipate in continuous improvement of UAT processes and methodologies.</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates, please email your resume to annasee@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Anna See Sing Yee</p><p>CEI Reg R25157535</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p></p>",
